quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  38,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  38,1,Saaad; wal-Qur-aani ziz zikr
  38,2,Balil lazeena kafaroo fee 'izzatilnw wa shiqaaq
  38,3,Kam ahlaknaa min qablihim min qarnin fanaadaw wa laata heena manaas
  38,4,Wa 'ajibooo an jaaa'a hum munzirum minhum wa qaalal kaafiroona haazaa saahirun kazzaab
  38,5,Aja'alal aalihata Ilaahanw Waahidan inna haazaa lashai'un 'ujaab
  38,6,Wantalaqal mala-u minhum anim shoo wasbiroo 'alaaa aalihatikum innna haazaa lashai 'uny yuraad
  38,7,Maa sami'naa bihaazaa fil millatil aakhirati in haazaaa illakh tilaaq
  38,8,'A-unzila 'alaihiz zikru mim baininaa; bal hum fee shakkim min Zikree bal lammaa yazooqoo 'azaab
  38,9,Am'indahum khazaaa 'inu rahmati Rabbikal 'Azeezil Wahhab
  38,10,Am lahum mulkus samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumaa falyartaqoo fil asbaab
  38,11,Jundum maa hunaalika mahzoomum minal Ahzaab
  38,12,Kazzabat qablahum qawmu Lootinw-wa 'Aadunw wa Fir'awnu zul awtaad
  38,13,Wa Samoodu wa qawmu Lootinw wa Ashaabul 'Aykah; ulaaa'ikal Ahzaab
  38,14,In kullun illaa kazzabar Rusula fahaqqa 'iqaab�(section 1)
  38,15,Wa maa yanzuru haaa ulaaa'i illaa saihatanw waahidatam maa lahaa min fawaaq
  38,16,Wa qaaloo Rabbanaa 'ajjil lanaa qittanaa qabla Yawmil Hisaab
  38,17,Isbir 'alaa maa yaqooloona wazkur 'abdanaa Daawooda zal aidi aidi innahooo awwaab
  38,18,Innaa sakhkharnal jibaala ma'ahoo yusabbihna bil'ashaiyi wal ishraaq
  38,19,Wattayra mahshoorah; kullul lahooo awwaab
  38,20,Wa shadadnaa mulkahoo wa aatainaahul Hikmata wa faslal khitaab
  38,21,Wa hal ataaka naba'ul khasm; iz tasawwarul mihraab
  38,22,Iz dakhaloo 'alaa Daawooda fafazi'a minhum qaaloo la takhaf khasmaani baghaa ba'dunaa 'alaa ba'din fahkum bainanaaa bilhaqqi wa laa tushtit wahdinaaa ilaa Sawaaa'is Siraat
  38,23,Inna haazaaa akhee lahoo tis'unw wa tis'oona na'jatanw wa liya na'jatunw waahidah; faqaala akfilneeha wa 'azzanee filkhitaab
  38,24,Qaala laqad zalamaka bisu 'aali na'jatika ilaa ni'aajihee wa inna kaseeram minal khulataaa'i la-yabghee ba'duhum 'alaa ba'din illal lazeena aamanoo wa 'amilus saalihaati wa qaleehum maa hum; wa zanna Daawoodu annamaa fatannaahu fastaghrara Rabbahoo wa kharra raaki'anw wa anaab
  38,25,Faghafarnaa lahoo zaalik; wa inna lahoo 'indanaa lazulfaa wa husna ma aab
  38,26,Yaa Daawoodu innaa ja'alnaaka khaleefatan fil ardi fahkum bainan naasi bilhaqqi wa laa tattabi'il hawaa fayudillaka 'an sabeelil laah; innal lazeena yadilloona 'an sabeelil laah; lahum 'azaabun shadeedum bimaa nasoo Yawmal Hisaab�(section 2)
  38,27,Wa ma khalaqnas samaaa'a wal arda wa maa bainahumaa baatilaa; zaalika zannul lazeena kafaroo; fawi lul lillazeena kafaroo minan Naar
  38,28,Am naj'alul lazeena aamanoo wa 'amilus saalihaati kalmufisdeena fil ardi am naj'alul muttaqeena kalfujjaar
  38,29,Kitaabun anzalnaahu ilaika mubaarakul liyaddabbarooo Aayaatihee wa liyatazakkara ulul albaab
  38,30,Wa wahabnaa li Daawooda Sulaimaan; ni'mal 'abd; innahoo awwaab
  38,31,Iz 'urida 'alaihi bil'ashiy yis saafinaatul jiyaad
  38,32,Faqaala inneee ahbabtu hubbal khairi 'an zikri Rabbee hattaa tawaarat bilhijaab
  38,33,Ruddoohaa 'alaiya fatafiqa masham bissooqi wal a'naaq
  38,34,Wa laqad fatannaa Sulaimaana wa alqainaa 'alaa kursiyyihee jasadan summa anaab
  38,35,Qaala Rabbigh fir lee wa hab lee mulkal laa yambaghee li ahadim mim ba'de inaka Antal Wahhab
  38,36,Fasakhkharnaa lahur reeha tajree bi amrihee rukhaaa'an haisu asaab
  38,37,Wash Shayaateena kulla bannaaa'inw wa ghawwaas
  38,38,Wa aakhareena muqarraneena fil asfaad
  38,39,Haazaa 'ataaa'unaa famnun aw amsik bighairi hisaab
  38,40,Wa inna lahoo 'indanaa lazulfaa wa husna ma-aab�(section 3)
  38,41,Wazkur 'abdanaaa Ayyoob; iz naada Rabbahooo annee massaniyash Shaitaanu binus binw wa 'azaab
  38,42,Urkud birijlika haaza mughtasalum baaridunw wa sharaab
  38,43,Wa wahabnaa lahoo ahlahoo wa mislahum ma'ahum rahmatam minna wa zikraa li ulil albaab
  38,44,"Wa khuz biyadika dighsan fadrib bihee wa laa tahnas, innaa wajadnaahu saabiraa; ni'mal 'abd; innahooo awwaab"
  38,45,Wazkur 'ibaadanaaa Ibraaheema wa Is-haaqa wa Ya'qooba ulil-aydee walabsaar
  38,46,Innaaa akhlasnaahum bi khaalisatin zikrad daar
  38,47,Wa innahum 'indanaa laminal mustafainal akhyaar
  38,48,Wazkur Ismaa'eela wal Yasa'a wa Zal-Kifli wa kullum minal akhyaar
  38,49,Haazaa zikr; wa inna lilmuttaqeena lahusna ma aab
  38,50,Jannaati 'adnim mufat tahatal lahumul abwaab
  38,51,Muttaki'eena feehaa yad'oona feehaa bifaakihatin kaseeratinw wa sharaab
  38,52,Wa 'indahum qaasiraatut tarfi atraab
  38,53,Haaza maa too'odoona li Yawmil Hisaab
  38,54,Inna haazaa larizqunaa maa lahoo min nafaad
  38,55,Haazaa; wa inna littaagheena lasharra ma-aab
  38,56,Jahannama yaslawnahaa fai'sal mihaad
  38,57,Haazaa falyazooqoohu hameemunw wa ghassaaq
  38,58,Wa aakharu min shak liheee azwaaj
  38,59,Haazaa fawjum muqtahimum ma'akum laa marhabam bihim; innahum saalun Naar
  38,60,Qaaloo bal antum laa marhabam bikum; antum qaddamtumoohu lanaa fabi'sal qaraar
  38,61,Qaaloo Rabbanaa man qaddama lanaa haaza fazidhu 'azaaban di'fan fin Naar
  38,62,Wa qaaloo ma lanaa laa naraa rijaalan kunnaa na'udduhum minal ashraar
  38,63,Attakhaznaahum sikh riyyan am zaaghat 'anhumul absaar
  38,64,Inna zaalika lahaqqun takhaasumu Ahlin Naar�(section 4)
  38,65,Qul innamaaa ana munzirunw wa maa min ilaahim illal laahul Waahidul Qahhaar
  38,66,Rabbus samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumal 'Azeezul Ghaffaar
  38,67,Qul huwa naba'un 'azeem
  38,68,Antum 'anhu mu'ridoon
  38,69,Maa kaana liya min 'ilmim bilmala il a'laaa iz yakhtasimoon
  38,70,Iny-yoohaaa ilaiya illaaa annnamaaa ana nazeerum mubeen
  38,71,Iz qaala Rabbuka lilmalaaa'ikati innee khaaliqum basharam min teen
  38,72,Fa-iza sawwaituhoo wa nafakhtu feehi mir roohee faqa'oo lahoo saajideen
  38,73,Fasajadal malaaa'ikatu kulluhum ajma'oon
  38,74,Illaaa Iblees; istakbara wa kaana minal kaafireen
  38,75,Qaala yaaa Ibleesu maa man'aka an tasjuda limaa khalaqtu biyadai; astakbarta am kunta min 'aaleen
  38,76,Qaala ana khairum minah; khalaqtanee min naarinw wa khalaqtahoo min teen
  38,77,Qaala fakhruj minhaa fainnaka rajeem
  38,78,Wa inna 'alaika la'nateee ilaa Yawmid Deen
  38,79,Qaala Rabbi fa anzirneee ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon
  38,80,Qaala fa innaka minal munzareen
  38,81,Ilaa Yawmil waqtil ma'loom
  38,82,Qaala fabi'izzatika la ughwiyannahum ajma'een
  38,83,Illaa 'ibaadaka minhumul mukhlaseen
  38,84,"Qaala falhaqq, walhaqqa aqool"
  38,85,La amla'annna Jahannama minka wa mimman tabi'aka minhum ajma'een
  38,86,Qul maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrinw wa maaa ana minal mutakallifeen
  38,87,In huwa illaa zikrul lil'aalameen
  38,88,Wa lata'lamunna naba ahoo ba'da heen�(section 5)
